efficiency: HIGH
time complexity: O(log n)
space complexity: O(1)
energy implications: LOW
explanation: Compute a mask that has all bits set up to the most significant bit of n, then XOR with n to flip every bit. This avoids string conversion and uses only bitwise operations.

